  "text": "where corner points are to be counted with multiplicity [CITATION_1] . We extend the definition of Euler measure to 2-chains linearly. Let n y (P) be the sum of the local multiplicities of P at the points y i ∈ y. By [24, Proposition 7.5], c 1 (s z (y)), H(P) = χ(P) + 2n y (P).",
